|\frac{x^4-y^4}{x^2+y^2}|<\epsilon\\ \frac{|x^4-y^4|}{x^2+y^2}<\epsilon\\ |x^4-y^4|<\epsilon(x^2+y^2)\\ \frac{|x^4-y^4|}{\epsilon}<x^2+y^2\\ \frac{1}{\epsilon}<x^2+y^2\\ x^2+y^2>\frac{1}{\epsilon}\\ \sqrt{x^2+y^2}>\sqrt{\frac{1}{\epsilon}}
